      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOHO HUDSON (1) made it two wins from his last three outings two months ago, getting home by 4 metres over 1609m at Menangle. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Finds a suitable assignment and will be a major force once more. GOOD BOOTS BINDI (8) had been building to a win and it arrived last time out when successful over 2190m at this track, getting home by a nose after leading. Drawn to enjoy a nice run, with luck possibly playing a role at some point. Meets a comparable field and she can make it two on the trot. MODERN GINGER (9) is heading the right way, improving last time out to finish second here over 2190m. Genuine threat. AVOCA BLUES (4) is in the mix following a respectable second at his most recent appearance over 1800m at Kapunda. Top-three aspirations.",
